Project Dependency Graph

Dependency Tree

  • com.github.quickhull3d:quickhull3d:jar:1.0.0-SNAPSHOT
    A Robust 3D Convex Hull Algorithm in Java

    Description: This is a 3D implementation of QuickHull for Java, based on the original paper by Barber, Dobkin, and Huhdanpaa and the C implementation known as qhull. The algorithm has O(n log(n)) complexity, works with double precision numbers, is fairly robust with respect to degenerate situations, and allows the merging of co-planar faces.

    URL: https://github.com/Quickhull3d/quickhull3d

    Project License: GNU LESSER GENERAL PUBLIC LICENSE (LGPL) version 3
